# ReversingLabs TitaniumScale

This app supports using ReversingLabs Advanced File Analysis to 'detonate file' on the TitaniumScale
Advanced Malware Analysis Appliance.  
  
The ReversingLabs TitaniumScale Appliance is powered by TitaniumCore, the malware analysis engine
that performs automated static analysis using the Active File Decomposition technology.  
  
TitaniumCore unpacks and recursively analyzes files without executing them, and extracts internal
threat indicators to classify files and determine their threat level. TitaniumCore is capable of
identifying thousands of file format families. It recursively unpacks hundreds of file format
families, and fully repairs extracted files to enable further analysis.  
  
For more information, consult the [official product
website.](https://www.reversinglabs.com/products/malware-analysis-solution.html)
